<P N="22">22. Take pure nitre one drachm, crabs claws two drachms, &s;yrup of mar&s;h|mallows one ounce, barley water ten ounces. Mix.</P>
<P N="23">23. Take ra&s;ping of &s;a&s;&s;afra&s;s two ounces, of the three &s;aunders, of each two drachms, powder of liquori&s;h one ounce. Mix. Infu&s;e for tea.</P>
