<PB N="112" REF="015100_0111_0F95D2EEAAE696F8">
half an hour in milk three pounds; &s;train: Add, honey, one ounce and a half. Mix</P>
<P N="64">64 Take &s;pirit of &s;curvy-gra&s;s two ounces, elixir proprietatis Paracel&s;i one ounce. Mix.</P>
<P N="65">65 Take &s;pirit of &s;ea &s;alt one drachm, honey of ro&s;es one ounce and a half, com|mon water five ounces. Mix.</P>
